{"tid":1662924,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學]分享實時位置 以防被消失! (Telegram/Whatsapp)","createTime":"2019-10-19T05:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T05:59:27.000Z","uid":94677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"138f09b3821fba963cdadfe68fc0332ff5902042","tid":1662924,"uid":94677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">近排太多人疑似被消失/離奇失蹤/死因無可疑<br />\n被捕既人又無辦法話比人知捉左去邊 好彩既去到警署先沒收手機/強逼關機<br />\n以下分享實時位置方法只適合用於你同你<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">最信任</span></ins></strong>既朋友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQq6Ywp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQq6Ywp.png&h=5e4bbfa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qze7HYr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQze7HYr.png&h=1ec5ef9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此方法有效第一時間比友人知道你實時位置 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔建議分享自己實時位置去大量人既群組非常危險 以防比鬼跟+害死身邊人+被CAP圖<br />\n建議單對單/係少人群組分享 最好大家互相分享 以防有詐/確認大家位置<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果見到對方突然熄左實時位置請大家注意 有可能當事人已經被捕 手機被沒收+關機 </span><br />\n用完請記得關定位 刪紀錄 報平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此方法唔係100%安全 有一定風險 但起碼有保障<br />\n歡迎補充</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">另求介紹線上/電腦軟件執圖/做宣傳用 唔洗專業軟件<br />\n普通有整齊排版 插圖/字 加符號 要日後可以再編輯圖/字</span>"},{"pid":"f907d2d71dd8a7452d89aee45e69926395d70199","tid":1662924,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>全日 全民宣傳日</strong></span> <br />\n- 宣傳1020民陣大遊行<br />\n[ 各區宣傳，嗌口號，貼文宣，Airdrop ]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1900 - 2030 國際人道救援祈禱會</strong></span><br />\n- 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n[已